{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban the automatic renewal of contracts for insurance products",
        "additional_details": "Disadvantaged people in particular can be at a greater risk of paying higher premiums due to this practice. I have had to contact a company via phone, rather than being able to cancel a contract online, left me even more out of pocket.",
        "background": "Many insurance companies use automatic renewal of contracts to increase prices and make it difficult to cancel policies. This can cost consumers hundreds of pounds.",
